name: DOR ADMONI
description: DOR ADMONI (XDORX) represents freedom, liberty, nobility, music, dance, and love. It embodies order and purity, the protection of the weak, the pleasures of life, and the wisdom to set true boundaries while knowing how to be content with what is right and permitted. It carries the essence of peace, tranquility, nature, the flavors of life, laughter, smiles, and love — all safeguarded by the strongest and noblest protection. The project also advocates for empowering women’s self-confidence, equality of their rights, and recognition of their status across the world.
